<br>
i guess what i gathered up was that phytir had been playing NWN and had basically ditched EQ and low and behold he logs in and finds a mob that holds a very nice aggro gaining tool in which he thought he could use. yes he could use it but then later when he logged how long would it be since we would see him again?<br>
