is the willsapper that great of a weapon? hell no but it is a great tool &quot;notice i said tool earlier is that is the purpose of it&quot;. vanikii is a pushover for our guild but yet still drops a very nice weapon which can be used for our warriors to regain aggro easier for us poor monks who don’t FD evade enough =P.<br>
