imo Wilo is the person to place blame upon, it was NOT his toon, and for him to tell a guildie and that guildie also being an officer to &quot;STFU&quot; over guild chat only makes me mad that a leader did not GR his ass instead of letting him do it himself..... i guess the good part is that he is gone....<br>
