<br>
for those of you bashing tindi do you even know what you are talking about? do you know how hard it is to run a raiding guild, or manage a GMS system, delegate to the other guilds on our server, or any other acts in which our guild leaders are basically demanded to engage with on a day by day basis in which mistakes can and will be made.... imo they handled this very well and again the only mistake was not to GR his ass sooner....<br>
<br>
one last thing, people who get pissed off over loot are shallow and im glad they get weeded out of tindi. yes it is cool when you are the 1st to loot X item, or X item for your class but is it that important to forfeit everything you have worked to do for your guild? loot comes and goes, it gets more common and it gets better. the *only* exception i could think of is within an artifact, or say mobs like the warders in which they will never respawn in which case their loot is gone forever &quot;the item that comes to my mind the most would be the gnome mask as that is a status symbol that will most likely never be achieved by most other people on our server&quot;. it is a computer-generated image and if that is what truly makes you happy in your life as it must be sad.... im sorry douche bag<br>
